      <section id="id3831295">
        <title>ACTIVITY: To perform mental calculations [LO 1.9.1, LO 1.9.2]</title>
        <para id="id4860387">1. In Mathematics it is important to be able to think fast. Let’s see how quick you are in your first mental arithmetic test in Grade 6. Work as quickly and as accurately as possible.</para>
