      <section id="id6759002">
        <title>2. Let’s count</title>
        <para id="id4502116">Work with a friend and take turns to count in:</para>
        <para id="id4875570">2.1 tens from 19 870 to 20 040</para>
        <para id="id6250525">2.2 hundreds from 67 403 backwards to 65 903</para>
        <list id="id3332314" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>thousands from 37 556 backwards to 29 556</item>
          <item>ten thousands from 25 526 to 95 526</item>
